  "Life expectancy at birth, total (years)",
  "Prevalence of anemia among children (% of children ages 6-59 months)",
  "Prevalence of overweight, weight for height (% of children under 5)",

  filter(grepl("SH.DYN.MORT", Indicator.Code))
csv_filtered <- csv %>%
  filter(grepl("SH.DYN.MORT", Indicator.Code))

# Pivotar para formato longo apenas com anos >= 2010
csv_long <- csv_filtered %>%
  pivot_longer(
    cols = starts_with("X"),        # Seleciona todas as colunas de anos
    names_to = "Year",
    values_to = "Value"
  ) %>%
  mutate(Year = as.integer(sub("X", "", Year))) %>%  # Remove o "X" e transforma em n√∫mero
  filter(Year >= 2010)                               # Filtra anos a partir de 2010

# Criar o boxplot
ggplot(csv_long, aes(x = factor(Year), y = Value)) +  # factor para organizar no eixo X
  geom_boxplot(fill = "skyblue", color = "darkblue") +
  labs(
    title = "Distribui√ß√£o dos Indicadores SH.DYN.MORT por Ano",
    x = "Ano",
    y = "Valor do Indicador"
  ) +
  theme_minimal()
